name: Our mate Marmite
description:
A digitisation of my now-sold original painting 'Our mate Marmite' - due to a dietary choice in the UK some years ago I had to grow to love Marmite. It wasn’t easy. Now though it does remind me of that time and so forms a focus for memory. And, like memories, I don’t need to access it ‘everyday’ as the series suggests but instead about once a month. On hot toast. With lots, and lots, of butter
3862 X 3860 PNG
